document.getElementsByClassName(); returns a node list (array lite) cant use forEach on a list
document.getElementsByTagName();
document.querySelector(); select using css selectors, multiple selectors e.g a class will return the first thing found querySelector returns ONE thing
document.querySelectorAll(); selects everything e.g a class all object are selected

